.000Z","msg":"歷史上黎講係事實<br />\n<br />\n但現實生活上大部份香港人<br />\n都唔會想被人當做中國人<br />\n<br />\n一黎文化唔同 二黎你班中國人出到國永遠都講普通話 個世界觀永遠得中國好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三黎每年五萬支那人入黎香港搶資源呀 <br />\n<br />\n你班中國人真係神憎鬼厭 俾人話係中國人真係慘撚過死<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gzTC5Qj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgzTC5Qj.jpg&h=e60a3534&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5b785f08c08da073fe0f4157a246ac7ba7da77f","tid":1125484,"uid":16404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T01:44:06.000Z","msg":"新浪活動大家知咩事啦"},{"pid":"31940e943ee830f6719a0268b66e74b48809179f","tid":1125484,"uid":192517,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T01:47:28.000Z","msg":"正臭西"},{"pid":"41c25c41b082dbd4054c3b6b427ad71f061141e4","tid":1125484,"uid":213252,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T02:01:22.000Z","msg":"好玻璃 留言同佢講翻咪得 洗唔洗dislike<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你仲要鬧埋佢 成個小朋友咁"},{"pid":"57b030db341c55ffb0f2943b65276735af6810ef","tid":1125484,"uid":135866,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T02:19:32.000Z","msg":"屌鳩一個日本人都唔會令到香港獨立<br />\n醒吓啦香港人<br />\n繼續返工啦"},{"pid":"9d7534f5f0cd436a68cbce6491de57713d97d1be","tid":1125484,"uid":201158,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T02:38:17.000Z","msg":"日本咪又係中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b124224c516fae5641c1767e6ede28fad3d5d1","tid":1125484,"uid":143402,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T02:41:24.000Z","msg":"玻璃心香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088673413788aeb3ea39df9f4272bbdd5e3f423b","tid":1125484,"uid":3358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T02:59:35.000Z","msg":"用佢角度諗：人地國家既事關我撚事咩"},{"pid":"410c2fae3ea9f3212ca987e85